<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .otp {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ff5722;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999999;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>NikoNiko</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear User,</p>
        <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) is:</p>
        <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        <p>Please use this OTP to complete your registration process. Do not share this code with anyone.</p>
        <p>Thank you for using NikoNiko!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
